hest cavity.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.060111,0.10359,0.099332,0.10409,0.093829,0.089498,0.091204,0.081748,0.077156,0.080021,0.067097,0.052321],"unified_progress":[0.04461,0.079671,0.09216,0.10366,0.10153,0.09914,0.097051,0.09088,0.08501,0.085545,0.067154,0.053593]},{"section":6,"text":"The fact that they found a lesion in the right lower lobe makes me think it's a specific type of abnormal growth or structure in the lung.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.058277,0.088571,0.092979,0.09868,0.093639,0.091136,0.092095,0.086294,0.081958,0.081944,0.072536,0.061891],"unified_progress":[0.046249,0.07412,0.086777,0.096981,0.097511,0.097515,0.096966,0.093869,0.089214,0.086309,0.073472,0.061016]},{"section":7,"text":"The lesion is nonfunctioning, which means it's not working like normal lung tissue.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.051806,0.074758,0.08548,0.091689,0.094768,0.095945,0.096052,0.093028,0.089219,0.083786,0.076359,0.06711],"unified_progress":[0.048118,0.070281,0.082389,0.089782,0.094724,0.098223,0.0966,0.095958,0.092361,0.088602,0.077993,0.06497]},{"section":8,"text":"Also, it's served by its own vessels, separate from the adjacent lung's vessels.","dimension":1,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.047953,0.067823,0.080827,0.090738,0.095429,0.098629,0.099126,0.096362,0.091448,0.084554,0.078034,0.069076],"unified_progress":[0.046684,0.06835,0.081002,0.089649,0.094887,0.097383,0.096386,0.095364,0.09468,0.088386,0.079455,0.067774]},{"section":9,"text":"That makes me think it's a tumor because tumors often have their own blood supply.","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.046096,0.063617,0.077116,0.087344,0.092855,0.096245,0.099614,0.098101,0.095245,0.092522,0.080673,0.070572],"unified_progress":[0.041189,0.063939,0.080537,0.091063,0.095276,0.10035,0.10003,0.098178,0.094617,0.091597,0.079077,0.064139]},{"section":10,